{
  "stem": "27335.7",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were-- there were-- many, many of them were saved-- saved this-- this way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we had a cow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because [NON-ENGLISH] family, being a-- a minister and so on, they had a small little farm.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And just a small farm and a few cows.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just before-- just before-- just before the-- the city was encircled, the men we had out there, they formed And so led the cow into-- into the city and put-- put the cow into the gutters because the garage was-- was confiscated by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So and he brought enough-- enough hay-- hay and that there was still milk to deliver, that we have milk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even that we took over then, for the children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then-- then came a-- came a, a condition situation what of you couldn't even-- even get-- get close to it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was right through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right through.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The raid-- the last-- last day was when I left the hosts in February 15.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well now '40-- that was in '45.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or that was the time where-- when the last battle took place on Sunday, Sunday afternoon, and Sunday-- Sunday night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Monday morning, it was at 10 o'clock came the Soviet blitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Spreading the city with leaflets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] And greeting the city, you are free.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Be calm and so on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And start to-- to readjust and restart your life and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- and-- the-- at the end of the following day, there came-- came a-- a-- a Red Army patrol with a Hungarian man with a-- with a red arm band and so.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody from the age of 16 to 60, we were driven out to dig out a-- a tank.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
